Content of Post: JUST IN: Absolute divorce bill approved on third and final reading by the House of Representatives. 126 voted in favor of the measure, 109 voted against it, and 20 abstained. | via Vivienne Gulla, ABS-CBN News

Content of Post: The House of Representatives approves on second reading HB 9349, which seeks to reinstitute absolute divorce as an alternative mode for the dissolution of marriage. | via Willard Cheng, ABS-CBN News
